WEBVTT

00:02.653 --> 00:04.329
Sheldon, your food's
getting cold.

00:04.331 --> 00:05.747
I'll eat later.

00:05.749 --> 00:06.949
Right now, I'm suckling

00:06.951 --> 00:09.284
at the informative bosom
of mother physics.

00:10.320 --> 00:13.154
It's hot when
Sheldon talks dirty.

00:14.991 --> 00:18.427
So, I found this Web site
where you send them pictures,

00:18.429 --> 00:19.594
they sculpt your head

00:19.596 --> 00:21.596
and make an action figure
out of you.

00:21.598 --> 00:22.597
How awesome is that?

00:22.599 --> 00:23.715
Oh, let me see.

00:23.717 --> 00:24.800
Yeah, you can pick
your wardrobe.

00:24.802 --> 00:26.468
You can even choose
your accessories.

00:26.470 --> 00:27.636
(chuckles)

00:27.638 --> 00:31.473
Leonard, you can get
a little asthma inhaler.

00:32.442 --> 00:33.775
Oh, this is neat.

00:33.777 --> 00:35.310
Think about all
the action figures

00:35.312 --> 00:36.511
we've bought over the years.

00:36.513 --> 00:39.281
It would be kind of cool
to have ones that look like us.

00:39.283 --> 00:40.515
Don't you think?

00:43.369 --> 00:45.237
Yeah, if that's your idea
of what's cool,

00:45.239 --> 00:47.188
you should get one.

00:47.190 --> 00:49.541
Yeah, so, I'm out.

00:50.860 --> 00:52.244
What do you think,
Sheldon?

00:52.246 --> 00:54.162
Want an action figure
that looks just like you?

00:54.164 --> 00:56.064
Would it come with kung-fu grip?

00:56.066 --> 00:57.432
No.

00:57.434 --> 00:59.584
Don't waste my time.

01:00.803 --> 01:03.672
You get that these are
personalize action figures.

01:03.674 --> 01:06.008
Honey, if you want one,
just get one.

01:06.010 --> 01:07.309
You're still
out, right?

01:07.311 --> 01:09.394
Yep.

01:09.396 --> 01:12.931
♪ Our whole universe
was in a hot, dense state ♪

01:12.933 --> 01:16.818
♪ Then nearly 14 billion years
ago expansion started... Wait! ♪

01:16.820 --> 01:18.353
♪ The Earth began to cool

01:18.355 --> 01:20.906
♪ The autotrophs began to drool,
Neanderthals developed tools ♪

01:20.908 --> 01:23.141
♪ We built the Wall
♪ <i>We built the pyramids</i> ♪

01:23.143 --> 01:25.861
♪ Math, Science, History,
unraveling the mystery ♪

01:25.863 --> 01:27.913
♪ That all started
with a big bang ♪

01:27.915 --> 01:29.564
♪ <i>Bang!</i> ♪

01:29.565 --> 01:33.565
<font color=#00FF00>♪ The Big Bang Theory 6x14 ♪</font>
<font color=#00FFFF>The Cooper/Kripke Inversion</font>
